                 Method signature:
                </td>
                <td class="statText">
                 int returnTime(int N, String[] buses)
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                 (be sure your method is public)
                </td>
               </tr>
              </table>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText">
             </td>
            </tr>
